    "@type": "LearningResource",
    "name": "Introduction to Galaxy and Sequence analysis",
    "description": "This learning path provides a foundational introduction to the Galaxy platform and the analysis of sequencing data. It guides users through common first steps in genome analysis, including quality control and mapping/assembly of genomic sequences. This resource is ideal for individuals new to Galaxy and/or the field of genomics, offering a structured approach to building essential skills. Tutorials are presented in a logical order, with a recommendation to start with slides before proceeding to hands-on exercises.",
